<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA526_03_SU_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema526_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema526_03_su_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="11" data-text="창의+">
            <div>
                <span lang="y">우리 모둠이 지난달에 읽은 책 수를 조사하고, 우리 모둠이 지난달에 읽은 책 수의 평균은 몇 권인지 구해 봅시다.</span>
                <button type="button" class="btn calculator">계산기</button>
            </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">우리 모둠이 지난달에 읽은 책 수를 조사하여 표로 나타내어 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="input_wrap">
            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
            <div class="example_box">
              <p lang="y">학생별 지난달에 읽은 책 수</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="table_box">
            <table>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th lang="y">이름</th>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="윤호" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="주아" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="은찬" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="가은" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th lang="y">책 수(권)</th>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="4" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="8" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">우리 모둠이 지난달에 읽은 책 수의 평균은 몇 권인가요? 다른 모둠의 평균과 비교해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span lang="y">권</span>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble_box">
            <span lang="y">
              우리 모둠이 책을<br>
              가장 많이 읽었네.
            </span>
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA526_03_SU/0006_content.svg" alt="">
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true" data-check="true">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
